Installation
~~~~~~~~~~~~

The 'mwe' package has due to its nature a little uncommon installation requirements.
While the normal package files are installed as normal, a variety of image files
are installed in the 'tex/latex/mwe/' folder, so that they can be accessed from
every (MWE) document.

The files should be installed in the following subdirectories of the TEXMF tree.
A TDS ZIP file which only needs to be unzipped over the TEXMF is also provided.
If 'mwe' is installed over a TeX distribution package manager like TeX Live or MikTeX,
no manual installation is required by the end-user.

      =======================================================================
         Files                                  TEXMF Installation folder
      -----------------------------------------------------------------------
         mwe.dtx mwe.ins                        source/latex/mwe/
         mwe.pdf README INSTALL                 doc/latex/mwe/
         mwe.sty                                tex/latex/mwe/
         *.pdf *.png *.jpg *.eps                tex/latex/mwe/
         image-*x*.{tex,pdf,png,jpg,eps}        tex/latex/mwe/
         image-?.{tex,pdf,png,jpg,eps}          tex/latex/mwe/
         image-golden*.{tex,pdf,png,jpg,eps}    tex/latex/mwe/
         image-a?*.{pdf,png,jpg,eps}            tex/latex/mwe/
         image-letter*.{pdf,png,jpg,eps}        tex/latex/mwe/
         image-a?*.tex image-letter*.tex        source/latex/mwe/
      =======================================================================

